{"tid":1725400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"推俾民記見到 抗爭紀律條款","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T18:22:06.000Z","uid":186521,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc67717c316d3b10ad21dec602baa0c63ea0f7c","tid":1725400,"uid":186521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n無論裝修 神獸<br />\n大家傾傾有咩紀律條款<br />\n好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如<br />\n1. 黑先裝修<br />\n2. 遇藍可勸可忽視 郁手先神獸<br />\n3. 冇popo時不可隨意火魔<br />\n4. 不可使用危險性物品 例如gas 氧氣鑵 防止team kill自己人<br />\n5. 裝飾不用火<br />\n6. 絕不影響民居<br />\n7. 絕不獅鳥記者FA 除非佢做衰嘢 即使係紅媒<br />\n<br />\n大家諗諗仲有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c8dcf32b4c0235cae32f35d5cd70fb1c867856","tid":1725400,"uid":143341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"紀律條款？ 咁如果有手足犯規咁點<br />\n搵糾察捉佢哋？定係叫警甴拉人？"},{"pid":"5e9c0e1cb8e5834687b22a5eb1aab40db9ab9fbd","tid":1725400,"uid":62714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47c8dcf32b4c0235cae32f35d5cd70fb1c867856","tid":1725400,"uid":143341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"紀律條款？ 咁如果有手足犯規咁點<br />\n搵糾察捉佢哋？定係叫警甴拉人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"自我約束<br />\n要發洩嘅就搵班狗嚟發洩"},{"pid":"0924bc24c412b1ecaa820234554c342911605396","tid":1725400,"uid":73649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n咪on9<br />\n想做大台"},{"pid":"cb476b3ae65ded2042dbf5b43c28592900cc4a19","tid":1725400,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"根本冇用 之前顔色都冇跟"},{"pid":"b94746174174a3f3cba0740088697dc41832cf4c","tid":1725400,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:49:40.000Z","msg":"唔好企圖用規則將示威定型<br />\n一定型就好易俾對家捉到路利用，呢個禮拜大家有眼睇<br />\n一切靠大家嘅良知紀律自規就算"},{"pid":"c0c7214b3